OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1783521450
OL,3,CTour of Britain route revealed
OL,4,Cincluding Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,5,Cstages
OL,7,FThe world's best cyclists will take on
OL,8,Fthe 900km route across five stages
OL,9,Ffrom 2-6 September.
OL,11,FThey'll start in Lincolnshire, make
OL,12,Ftheir way through Yorkshire, before
OL,13,Ffinishing in the Scottish Borders.
OL,15,FStage One ` Lincoln-Lincoln `
OL,16,FWednesday 2 September
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1783521450
OL,3,CTour of Britain route revealed
OL,4,Cincluding Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,5,Cstages
OL,7,FRiders head out into the Lincolnshire
OL,8,FWolds as they exit the city of
OL,9,FLincoln, making their way through
OL,10,FMarket Rasen before hitting the routes
OL,11,Fmost northernmost point, heading
OL,12,Fthrough the town of Caistor in the
OL,13,FWest Lindsey District.
OL,15,FThe route makes its way past
OL,16,FWaddingham, before turning west
OL,17,Ftowards Ingham before heading back
OL,18,Ftowards Lincoln.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1783521450
OL,3,CTour of Britain route revealed
OL,4,Cincluding Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,5,Cstages
OL,7,FThe riders will then tackle the climb
OL,8,Fof Michaelgate five times on a final
OL,9,Fcircuit in the city centre after
OL,10,Fnearly 120km of racing, taking in the
OL,11,Frenowned Lincoln Grand Prix circuit, a
OL,12,Fcornerstone of the Lloyds National
OL,13,FRoad Series.
OL,15,FStage Two ` Boston-Skegness ` Thursday
OL,16,F3 September
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1783521450
OL,3,CTour of Britain route revealed
OL,4,Cincluding Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,5,Cstages
OL,7,FFrom the start in Boston, the peloton
OL,8,Fwill ride past Coningsby ` the home of
OL,9,Fthe Dambusters during World War Two,
OL,10,Fwho were based at RAF Coningsby, which
OL,11,Fnow plays host to the Battle of
OL,12,FBritain Memorial Flight.
OL,14,FThe riders then head through Woodhall
OL,15,FSpa, Horncastle and Wragby, before
OL,16,Fheading east into the Lincolnshire
OL,17,FWolds, intersecting with the stage one
OL,18,Fcourse at Binbrook.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1783521450
OL,3,CTour of Britain route revealed
OL,4,Cincluding Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,5,Cstages
OL,7,FHeading down to Louth, before heading
OL,8,Fon to the coastal towns of Mablethorpe
OL,9,Fand Sutton-on-Sea, the race hits one
OL,10,Flast ascent near Langton Hill, before
OL,11,Fit drops down for a ferocious sprint
OL,12,Finto Skegness to decide the day two
OL,13,Fwinner.
OL,15,FStage Three ` Hull-Beverley ` Friday 4
OL,16,FSeptember
OL,18,FDeparting from Hull, the riders will
OL,19,Fface a 200km stage as they head out to
OL,20,Fthe east coast, through Withernsea, up
OL,21,Fto Hornsea, and onto Skipsea.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1783521450
OL,3,CTour of Britain route revealed
OL,4,Cincluding Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,5,Cstages
OL,7,FAs the race heads to Burton Agnes, a
OL,8,Fseries of climbs face the riders as
OL,9,Fthey head around to Driffield before
OL,10,Fheading downhill into Wetwang as the
OL,11,Frace gears up for an exciting climax.
OL,13,FOnce they reach Beverley, the riders
OL,14,Fwill face a 16km circuit with four
OL,15,Fpassages finishing with a testing
OL,16,Fuphill drag to the racecourse for its
OL,17,Fconclusion.
OL,19,FStage Four ` Helmsley-Leyburn `
OL,20,FSaturday 5 September
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1783521450
OL,3,CTour of Britain route revealed
OL,4,Cincluding Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,5,Cstages
OL,7,FStage four is expected to be a pivotal
OL,8,Fmoment in deciding the 2026 winner as
OL,9,Fthe riders take on the hardest stage
OL,10,Fof the tour.
OL,12,FStarting in the market town of
OL,13,FHelmsley in the North York Moors
OL,14,FNational Park, the race will head
OL,15,Fthrough Easingwold, Boroughbridge, and
OL,16,Fthe cathedral city of Ripon before
OL,17,Fentering the Yorkshire Dales National
OL,18,FPark.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1783521450
OL,3,CTour of Britain route revealed
OL,4,Cincluding Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,5,Cstages
OL,7,FA challenging climb out of Greenhow
OL,8,FBank out of Pateley Bridge paves the
OL,9,Fway for the peloton head to
OL,10,FGrassington, before it weaves its way
OL,11,Fup Wharfedale towards Buckden and Cray.
OL,13,FThe riders then climb Kidstones which
OL,14,Ffeatured in the 2014 Tour de France
OL,15,Fopening stage, before heading to
OL,16,FAysgarth Falls.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1783521450
OL,3,CTour of Britain route revealed
OL,4,Cincluding Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,5,Cstages
OL,7,FThe stage then tackles the climbs of
OL,8,FGreets Moss and Grinton Moor in quick
OL,9,Fsuccession, before the race reaches a
OL,10,Fconclusion in Leyburn which is hosting
OL,11,Fa finish to the Lloyds Tour of Britain
OL,12,Ffor the first time, on what is sure to
OL,13,Fbe a memorable day's racing.
OL,15,FStage Five ` Earlston-Earlston `
OL,16,FSunday 6 September
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1783521450
OL,3,CTour of Britain route revealed
OL,4,Cincluding Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,5,Cstages
OL,7,FDeparting towards Smailholm, the last
OL,8,Fstage heads towards Kelso, turning off
OL,9,Fjust before the town to take in Hume,
OL,10,FGreenlaw and Duns. A challenging
OL,11,Fsector then faces the riders in the
OL,12,FLammermuir Hills, passing Whiteadder
OL,13,FWater before a climb to Redstone Rig
OL,14,Fand Duddy Bank.
OL,16,FOnce the race heads back towards
OL,17,FEarlston, the riders have two circuits
OL,18,Fof a 19km lap before the race
OL,19,Fconcludes and the next Tour of Britain
OL,20,Fmen's champion is crowned.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1783521450
OL,3,CTour of Britain route revealed
OL,4,Cincluding Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,5,Cstages
OL,7,FDirector of Events for British Cycling
OL,8,FVentures, Jonathan Day, said: "It is
OL,9,Falways exciting to reveal the stage
OL,10,Froutes for the Lloyds Tour of Britain,
OL,11,Fit's the news fans have been waiting
OL,12,Ffor, so they can plan the best
OL,13,Fpositions to watch the world's best
OL,14,Friders in the UK.
OL,16,F"We have worked closely with all our
OL,17,Fstakeholders to design a fantastic
OL,18,Froute that will ignite the race and
OL,19,Fcreate a memorable spectacle for all
OL,20,Finvolved.
OL,26,@pD@_OUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1783521450
OL,3,CTour of Britain route revealed
OL,4,Cincluding Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,5,Cstages
OL,7,F"The Tours are one of the largest free
OL,8,Fto spectate events in Britain, so we
OL,9,Fare thrilled to be bringing the men's
OL,10,Froute from Lincolnshire, through East
OL,11,Fand North Yorkshire, all the way to
OL,12,FEarlston in the Scottish Borders.
OL,14,F"The route brings unique challenges to
OL,15,Fthe riders, while delivering a
OL,16,Fbackdrop which shows the best of
OL,17,FBritain, from the beautiful coastline,
OL,18,Facross the highways, through our
OL,19,Fstunning countryside, and up some
OL,20,Ficonic and challenging categorised
OL,21,Fclimbs."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
